WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.720
Today Dad skipped work and talked with me all day.

00:06.360 --> 00:07.740
He’s a kind Dad.

00:08.500 --> 00:12.220
I wonder if I’ll make friends if I went to a different school.

00:13.090 --> 00:15.530
I wonder if school will be fun somewhere else.

00:16.610 --> 00:19.740
I wonder if I can go to the school Tomo-kun goes to.
